title: The Kitchen on Court Street
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. New American diner-style restaurant and bar in downtown. Menu is all-day breakfast plus wraps, soups, sandwiches, tacos, salads, burgers. Has fresh squeezed juices. Vegan options are marked, and staff is versed in all dietary restrictions. Makes food from scratch utilizing fresh and local ingredients. Full bar 7am-2am.
